{"id": "art-1538", "label": "Art. 1538", "title": "Art. 1538", "slug": "art-1538", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1863901415\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2105\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1863901415\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 153<sup>8</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_764151389\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2104\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_764151389\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Membrii consiliului de supraveghere nu pot fi\nconcomitent membri ai directoratului. De asemenea, ei nu pot cumula calitatea\nde membru în consiliul de supraveghere cu cea de salariat al <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1333001755\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2103\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1333001755\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Prin actul constitutiv sau prin hot&#259;râre a\nadun&#259;rii generale a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span> se pot\nstabili <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;ii</span> specifice de profesionalism <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>independen&#355;&#259;</span>\npentru membrii consiliului de supraveghere. În aprecierea <span class=SpellE>independen&#355;ei</span>\nunui membru al consiliului de supraveghere vor fi avute în vedere criteriile\nprev&#259;zute la art. 138<sup>2</sup> alin. (2).</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1549433168\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2102\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1549433168\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Cu privire la drepturile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\n<span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iile</span> membrilor consiliului de\nsupraveghere, <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iile</span> art. 144<sup>1</sup>,\nart. 144<sup>2</sup> alin. (1) <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> (5), ale art.\n144<sup>3</sup>, 144<sup>4</sup> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>150</span><span style='color:black'> se aplic&#259; în\nmod corespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>"}